Oven Fresh Pastry Shop is the creation of B.D.P.L Fernando. Having been a top pastry chef for several years in the hotel industry, his passion to bring forth the rich and tasteful delights to the public drew him to start up his own restaurant. What started in 1996 as a small restaurant, “Oven Fresh” is now an established and well known name among everyone.

With a dedicated and friendly staff of over 65 men and women, we strive to provide the best quality food and service always. Our menu currently consists of a diverse selection from sweets, cakes & savories to burgers, rice & noodles among many others.

Comprising of a skilled and artistic staff, we accept orders for wedding structures, design cakes, shape cakes and even customized & personalized sponge creations.

Our dynamic catering team is equipped and ready to server any occasion. With the flexibility to provide you with a customized menu, we ensure our service blends smoothly with any event. Our fast food chain is Consist of five branches in Moratuwa, Kollupitiya, Angulana, Narahenpita and Ratmalana.

